* the best name for it is "centerless", not "social"
	* every media is social, the old broadcasting media too, hence that is not a distinguishing name
* the worst design mistake of them currently is that the users can block others to comment on their posts
	* this is the case with X and Facebook
	* users should be able to hide unwanted comments, but only for themselves, not for others, let others decide themselves